---
title: Summer Succotash-Stuffed Peppers with Lima Beans & Cracked Bulgur
description: Succotash is a staple of Southern cuisine, and for good reason: it celebrates the variety of Summer’s delicious bounty. Corn, lima beans, and tomatoes are at their peak right now, and we can think of no better way to enjoy them than with these stuffed peppers.
